<form action="/competition/form/Team_School_HKRGAgeGroupCompetitionform" method="POST"
    class="mx-sm-5">

    <br>
    <h1 style="color: #888888; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: 200;"><b>第63屆體育節 - 2020年全港藝術體操分齡比賽</b></h1>
    <h2 style="color: #888888; font-size:14pt; font-weight: 200;"><u><b>團體項目報名表(學校組)</b></u></h2>
    <br><br>

    <div class="form-group">
        <label style="font-size:12px;color:red;font-weight:bold">*必須填寫 *Must provide
        </label>
    </div>

    <fieldset>
        <legend style="color: #83a70c; font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px;">團體資料 Group Details<span
